archimate:Constraint.name: OIOUBL v.2.02
archimate:Constraint.documentation:
(Offentlig Information Online Universal Business Language) All businesses, including small businesses and small public institutions, are expected to support the basic procurement process.
OIOUBL is a Danish adaptation of the International Standard UBL 2.0 from the Organization for the Advancement of Structured Information Standards (OASIS) for Danish Business Requirements.
